Package com.sap.conn.idoc.jco

Contains the main factory class JCoIDoc and all JCo related interfaces of the SAP Java IDoc Library.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JCoIDocHandler
    The JCoIDocHandler processes an IDocDocumentList in an application specific way.
    JCoIDocHandlerFactory
    The JCoIDocHandlerFactory creates JCoIDocHandler instances.
    JCoIDocQueueHandler
    The JCoIDocQueueHandler should be implemented by an application in order to process incoming IDocs.
    JCoIDocServer
    JCoIDocServer is an extension of JCoServer and provides all additional abilities for IDoc related RFC server communication.
    JCoIDocServerContext
    The JCoIDocServerContext provides information about a currently incoming RFC server request.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JCoIDoc
    The SAP Java IDoc Library provides an API to send, receive and process IDocs.

Package com.sap.conn.idoc.jco Description

Contains the main factory class JCoIDoc and all JCo related interfaces of the SAP Java IDoc Library.

Note:
The implementations for the interfaces JCoIDocServer and JCoIDocServerContext in this package are exclusively provided by the SAP Java IDoc Library and must not be implemented by custom Java applications. Hence, adding a new method to these two interfaces is not considered as an incompatible modification.
IDoc handler and related handler factory interfaces from this package need to be implemented by Java applications that wish to receive and process IDocs and IDoc packages via RFC (JCo).
